{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 565,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 5287,
        "text": "Nous le marquerons sur le museau [nez].",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5288,
        "text": "Nous les avons éprouvés comme Nous avons éprouvé les propriétaires du verger qui avaient juré d'en faire la récolte au matin,",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5289,
        "text": "sans dire: «Si Allah le veut».",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5290,
        "text": "Une calamité de la part de ton Seigneur tomba dessus pendant qu'ils dormaient,",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5291,
        "text": "et le matin, ce fut comme si tout avait été rasé.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5292,
        "text": "Le [lendemain] matin, ils s'appelèrent les uns les autres:",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5293,
        "text": "«Partez tôt à votre champ si vous voulez le récolter».",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5294,
        "text": "Ils allèrent donc, tout en parlant entre eux à voix basse:",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5295,
        "text": "«Ne laissez aucun pauvre y entrer aujourd'hui».",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5296,
        "text": "Ils partirent de bonne heure décidés à user d'avarice [envers les pauvres], convaincus que cela était en leur pouvoir.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5297,
        "text": "Puis, quand ils le virent [le jardin], ils dirent: «vraiment, nous avons perdu notre chemin.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5298,
        "text": "Ou plutôt nous sommes frustrés».",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5299,
        "text": "Le plus juste d'entre eux dit: «Ne vous avais-je pas dit: Si seulement vous avez rendu gloire à Allah!»",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5300,
        "text": "Ils dirent: «Gloire à notre Seigneur! Oui, nous avons été des injustes».",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5301,
        "text": "Puis ils s'adressèrent les uns aux autres, se faisant des reproches.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5302,
        "text": "Ils dirent: «Malheur à nous! Nous avons été des rebelles.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5303,
        "text": "Nous souhaitons que notre Seigneur nous le remplace par quelque chose de meilleur. Nous désirons nous rapprocher de notre Seigneur».",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5304,
        "text": "Tel fut le châtiment; et le châtiment de l'au-delà est plus grand encore, si seulement ils savaient!",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5305,
        "text": "Les pieux auront auprès de leur Seigneur les Jardins du délice.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5306,
        "text": "Traiterons-Nous les soumis [à Allah] à la manière des criminels?",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5307,
        "text": "Qu'avez-vous? Comment jugez-vous?",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5308,
        "text": "Ou bien avez-vous un Livre dans lequel vous apprenez",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5309,
        "text": "qu'en vérité vous obtiendrez tout ce que vous désirez?",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5310,
        "text": "Ou bien est-ce que vous avez obtenu de Nous des serments valables jusqu'au Jour de la Résurrection, Nous engageant à vous donner ce que vous décidez?",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5311,
        "text": "Demande-leur qui d'entre eux en est garant?",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5312,
        "text": "Ou encore, est-ce qu'ils ont des associés? Eh bien, qu'ils fassent venir leurs associés s'ils sont véridiques!",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5313,
        "text": "Le jour où ils affronteront les horreurs [du Jugement] et où ils seront appelés à la Prosternation mais ils ne le pourront pas.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 68,
          "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 52
        },
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
